items.title: Awesome Salesforce
items.content_text:
### Table of Contents / Packages and Libraries supporting salesforce

*   [Apex Test Kit (⭐156)](https://github.com/apexfarm/ApexTestKit) - Apex Test Kit can help generate massive sObject data for Apex test classes. It is can help establish arbitrary levels of many-to-one, one-to-many relationships, and also generate field values based on simple rules automatically.
